  <brief_title>Interim PET/CT Guided Cycle Numbers of R-CHOP in DLBCL</brief_title>
  <official_title>Interim PET/CT Guided Cycle Numbers of R-CHOP in Patients With Diffuse Large B-cell Lymphoma: a Exploratory Phase II Study Study</official_title>
